Class InfoFileParser

java.lang.Object
com.stahocorp.etlprocess.transform.InfoFileParser
public class InfoFileParser
extends java.lang.Object
Parser class of an info files from morele.net website. It uses mostly jsoup to extract specific fields from html elements.
